ygData.msgSnippet: Actually, I had a time when I logged out, came back the next evening, had to run from Qeynos to Paw and THEN find my poor body.  Total game time about 6 hours.
ygData.messageBody:
Actually, I had a time when I logged out, came back the next evening, had to run
from Qeynos to Paw and THEN find my poor body. Total game time about 6 hours.
Foolish to be in that dungeon at Level 6? Yep! hehe

Sara, Povar server
